        <abstract> 
<p>Much interested in BS’s letter on gneiss ["Remarks on the geological relations of the gneiss of the Alps", <hi rend="italic">Edinburgh New Philos. J.</hi> 42 (1847): 186–7].</p>  
<p>Sends copy of <hi rend="italic">South America</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Has shown that lamination of metamorphic schists closely allied with cleavage.</p>
        </abstract>
